{
 "name": "RPlog_Sean_Dillon_Returns_to_Etti_IV",
 "title": "Sean Dillon Returns to Etti IV",
 "summary": "Prex Simone Drake, shadowed by her new bodyguard Shikh and her dog Duke, travels to the Etti IV spaceport to greet the returning Executive Officer Sean Dillon, crossing paths with the cold Imperial agent Alora Antieres along the way. Dillon, freshly back, congratulates Drake on her promotion and presses her for a full briefing on the Wookiee Chewbacca's kidnapping of Direx member Roark and the deal to hand Han Solo to Grand Moff Caldny. Retiring to the relative safety of Drake's living room, the two spar over strategy: Dillon wants to summon Leia Organa Solo to Etti as leverage, while Drake flatly refuses, judging it a needless risk to the lucrative Imperial alliance. Dillon graciously appears to concede and flatters her sharp mind before departing, but once he is gone Drake confides to Shikh that he gave in too easily and means none of it, bracing for a harder fight ahead.",
